      "description": "Looking for a reliable workhorse that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of faithful service, it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone seeking dependable transportation at a great value. It\u2019s a well-loved car with character that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go!",
